{"timestamp": "2025-12-04 12:15:38.494478", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Troubleshooting Diagnosis Report\n\nSummary of topology and intent\n- Spine–leaf SDN fabric: leaf_1, leaf_2 (each with two hosts in 10.0.0.0/24) and one spine_1.\n- All switches join management 20.0.0.0/24; SDN controller at 20.0.0.100 via OpenFlow.\n- Expected: controller programs flows to allow L2/L3 reachability among hosts in 10.0.0.0/24.\n\nFindings\n\n1) Reachability and dataplane symptoms\n- Host-to-host connectivity is broken, even within the same leaf:\n  - host_1_1 -> host_1_2: 100% loss, “Destination Host Unreachable”\n  - host_2_1 -> host_2_2: 100% loss, “Destination Host Unreachable”\n  - host_1_1 -> host_2_1: 100% loss, “Destination Host Unreachable”\n- ARP resolution failures observed:\n  - host_1_1 ip neigh shows 10.0.0.2 and 10.0.0.3 state FAILED.\n- Host IP configs are consistent:\n  - host_1_1 10.0.0.1/24, host_1_2 10.0.0.2/24, host_2_1 10.0.0.3/24, host_2_2 10.0.0.4/24 with on-link routes to 10.0.0.0/24.\n\n2) Control plane and switch state\n- All OVS bridges configured with controller tcp:20.0.0.100:6633; fail_mode: secure.\n- Controller connectivity status on all switches:\n  - is_connected=false; status last_error=\"Connection timed out\"; states CONNECTING/BACKOFF.\n- No OpenFlow rules installed:\n  - ovs-ofctl dump-flows on leaf_1, leaf_2, spine_1 returns only headers (no flows).\n- Ports are physically up:\n  - ovs-ofctl show indicates eth0/eth1/eth2 ports in LIVE state on all switches.\n  - Interface counters show links are up; no TX forwarding seen from OVS (consistent with drop-all behavior in secure mode without flows).\n- Management network is healthy:\n  - leaf_1, leaf_2, spine_1 can ping 20.0.0.100 successfully with low RTT, confirming IP reachability to controller host.\n\n3) Anomaly detection and impact\n- Anomaly: SDN controller session failure on all switches (OpenFlow TCP connection timeout) while IP reachability to the controller host is fine.\n- Because fail_mode=secure and there are no flows, switches drop all traffic, including ARP broadcasts. This causes complete loss of L2/L3 connectivity among hosts in 10.0.0.0/24.\n\nLocalization of the fault\n- Data-plane links and switch ports are up (LIVE), suggesting physical connectivity is not the primary issue.\n- The fault localizes to the OpenFlow control-plane connection between switches (leaf_1, leaf_2, spine_1) and the controller endpoint at 20.0.0.100:6633.\n- Hosts and management network are not at fault.\n\nRoot cause assessment\n- The switches can reach 20.0.0.100 at IP layer, but all report TCP timeouts to tcp/6633, indicating:\n  - The OpenFlow controller process is not running or not listening on 20.0.0.100:6633, or\n  - A port mismatch (e.g., controller listening on 6653 while switches target 6633), or\n  - A firewall/ACL blocking TCP/6633 on the controller host.\n- With no controller connection, no flows are installed and the secure fail mode enforces a dataplane drop of all traffic.\n\nKey evidence\n- Pings between hosts: Destination Host Unreachable (100% loss).\n- host_1_1 ip neigh: 10.0.0.2 and 10.0.0.3 FAILED.\n- ovs-vsctl list Controller on each switch: is_connected=false, last_error=\"Connection timed out\", target=\"tcp:20.0.0.100:6633\".\n- ovs-ofctl dump-flows: no flows present.\n- ovs-ofctl show: all data ports LIVE.\n- Switches ping controller IP successfully, confirming L3 reachability to 20.0.0.100.\n\nAssessment of network health\n- Overall health: Critical outage in the fabric dataplane due to control-plane failure. All host-to-host communication within 10.0.0.0/24 is impacted.\n- Management plane: Healthy (IP connectivity to the controller host is confirmed).\n- Faulty component: Controller service endpoint for OpenFlow at 20.0.0.100:6633 (service unavailable/misconfigured/blocked), not the OVS switches or physical links.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 13475, "output_tokens": 3235, "total_tokens": 16710, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 11648}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 2176}}}
